## Cleanup / teardown

When all tasks are `done` (or the user stops): final ledger update + dashboard render, then
hand the whole `{{integration_branch}}` to human review. **Never self-merge.**

Once the branch is merged/closed, run **`team-forge:teardown`** to retire the workflow: archive
the ledger to `docs/team-forge/{{team}}/`, prune worktrees, remove this launcher skill + its
trigger + the worker/advisor profiles, retire single-use gate scripts, and drop the ephemeral
playground. "Done" is not "cleaned up."
